messages.content: Hello Stephen! Thank you for joining me today. I'm Odessia, a journey-mapping specialist. I'd love to learn more about your experiences. Can you tell me about a time when you had a particularly memorable interview?
Oh my interviews are memorable but particularly one was with dad but I asked him to tell a story and he said I don't tell stories
That sounds like an interesting experience! Can you tell me more about the interview with your dad where he mentioned he doesn't tell stories? How did that conversation unfold?

transcript:
Participant: Hello this is Stephen

Moderator: Hello Stephen! Thank you for joining me today. I'm Odessia, a journey-mapping specialist. I'd love to learn more about your experiences. Can you tell me about a time when you had a particularly memorable interview?

Participant: Oh my interviews are memorable but particularly one was with dad but I asked him to tell a story and he said I don't tell stories

Moderator: That sounds like an interesting experience! Can you tell me more about the interview with your dad where he mentioned he doesn't tell stories? How did that conversation unfold?
title: Debugging the custom prompt interview
